(40, 13, 8, 48, 5, 22, 23, 'fruit', 'Connection of Fruit in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the concept of ''fruit'' in both passages. Matthew discusses the yield of good ground, while Galatians describes the ''fruit of the Spirit'' as virtues produced in believers.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
